column17:
The second tweet is using a distract tactic. Instead of discussing the topic of the economy, which is the focus of the coordinated campaign, the tweet brings up the violent attacks on democratic processes in Uganda and criticizes the EU for allegedly funding the government. This is a completely different topic and serves to divert attention away from the main focus on economic issues. 

Example of distract tactic: 
@EmmanuelMacron @alferdez The violent attacks on democratic processes through undermining rule of law in #Uganda by despot @KagutaMuseveni: have been neglected but rather funded by #EU a.k.a The Friends Of The Dictator. #UgMoving4wd #EndImpunityUG21 @IntlCrimCourt @coe @UN @UKParliament @Europarl_EN

